{
  "stem": "10644.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- we had-- we had to take examinations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I take the entrance examinations, and with my tests, my-- my--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From-- from the school, you know, I was admitted in 1927 to the medical school in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There, you know, you didn't go first to pre-med.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You would graduate medical school, and it is six years lasting medical school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is-- Lithuania, it was at that time, Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was at that time Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the closest-- the closest to me where I lived in Bialystok, the closest was Vilna.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had relatives.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could live there, you know, somehow sustain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was, you know, it was problem with sustain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have relatives there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They helped me when I was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was, at that time, the most respected, you know, profession for a Jewish-- for a Jewish young boy, you know, a young guy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right now.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't consider.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I will not advise my-- I'm glad that my sons didn't go into medicine, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Medicine is now here in the United States, with malpractices business, it's in the dog house, especially my specialty, obstetrics and gynecology, which was before, very, very respected-- respected became one of the worst specialties.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They help me very much but how-- as much they could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, they-- they had a small business, and they helped me with very little money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to-- to-- to be a teacher, you know, be tutoring-- tutoring to make-- to make my money in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you know, not salary-- everything from [INAUDIBLE] the high school and the-- not good in mathematics, fine, not good in-- in Polish language, fine, not good in Latin language, fine-- everything, you know.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Latin was one of the most important languages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- training.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- six year--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's brother from Vyazma, too, [? won-- ?] went to-- entered the gymnasia and then, you know, was admitted to Moscow medical school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he became a doctor, and-- and he became an obstetrician-gynecologist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then somehow, influenced-- oh, my uncle is in obstetrics, let me go and be in obstetrics.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is-- that is number one, and then, you know, just simple life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Life dictated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I graduated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to go for one year to Polish Army as a doctor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was involved in all the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the-- all the years-- all the years I was involved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Vilna, I was involved in-- in-- it was called, you know, the Union of Jewish Medical Students.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Polish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, in Polish it was-- it was [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Radovski ?] Club Medical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Something like this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the Polish didn't-- didn't accept us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had somehow had representation for the-- before the dean and-- and professors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you have to have a representation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we organize as a Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then maybe it was-- maybe the Poles-- the dean advised make-- make your own organization.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Educational, in the first-- [? first of all. ?] I was the-- I was the librarian at the beginning, and I was buying books, medical books for everyone.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How we've got money, we would organize balls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, balls.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A ball, you know, a--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dance, and [? dance ?] it was usually, the best, usually became the best usual dance evening in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was basically not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wouldn't come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] they were completely-- completely away from-- the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many didn't talk to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will not tell restrict.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, the professors were very-- very equal to all-- to all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was-- we were sitting on the left side in the-- left side in the--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were sitting on the right side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were 90 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were 25, 30, but that was how the division.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did-- didn't dare to go to their side, and they will not go to our side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, the first year of medicine is-- one of the main subjects is anatomy or histology, you know, microscopic anatomy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But for anatomy, you have to have cadavers to study, to-- to study all the organs and how it is built.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Polish students brought the conditions that they would not allow us to work on their Christian cadavers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Christian cadavers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had to get-- to get-- you know, to get-- when we went to Jewish hospital, they said, yes, from time to time, we have, you know, a poor man without a family died.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody-- nobody takes-- [INAUDIBLE] took care.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went-- but you see, the religious Jews would come right away and will take and give him a decent burial.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went, you know, to-- to the Rabbi of Vilna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Rabbi was Chaim Eizer Rodianski.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
